259dc175010d33dbd5e1a9261a37a1cf97cb4b75.query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Articles (
                id TEXT NOT NULL,
                source TEXT NOT NULL,
                title TEXT NOT NULL,
                sub_title TEXT NOT NULL,
                content TEXT NOT NULL,
                date DATETIME,
                PRIMARY KEY (id, source)
            )

a43893b2f56ec85c797a726db28768f8fac99873.query:
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO Articles (id, source, title, sub_title, content, date)
            VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)

ae76a7823f9a14ff2b8ad1d733b6aefbc8f5b3d5.query:
SELECT 
            id,
            source,
            title,
            sub_title,
            content,
            date
        FROM Articles
